  "title": "Receptionist x 2 | Tuition Centre | Queenstown / Telok Blangah",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Customer Service Officer x 2</strong></li><li><strong>Industry: Tuition Centre for Secondary Students</strong></li><li><strong>Working day: 5 Working Days (Off-day Fall On Weekdays)</strong></li><li><strong>Working hour:  1pm-9pm (Weekdays)/ 10am-8pm(Weekends)</strong></li><li><strong>Location: Alexandra Village [ Queenstown / Telok Blangah ]</strong></li><li><strong>Basic Salary: $2200 – $2600 [ Depends on Experience 0-3 Years ]</strong></li><li><strong>Entitled to Incentives & Bonus</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Open to entry level [ on the job training provided ] , those with customer service / receptionist experience is a plus.</strong></p><p><u><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Attending to customer’s enquiry via various modes (e.g. Phone call/ walk-in/ E-mail)</li><li>Promoting and educating customers on our programmes</li><li>Follow-up / inform customers and students of any upcoming programmes</li><li>Handling of various modes of payments (e.g. MasterCard/ Visa/ NETS/ Cheque/ Cash)</li><li>Tracking and maintenance of student attendance</li><li>Assist in coordination and allocation of students and classes</li><li>Other ad-hoc assignments when necessary</li></ul><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p></p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p><p></p>",
